{"tid":156374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭Ａ字膊本色盡現","createTime":"2017-03-14T16:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T06:47:40.000Z","uid":16970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfadb5ea728c6f4e9e340417c74128cd61a3823e","tid":156374,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"攞彩嘅時候，佢就會話「丁屋嘅問題係我作為發展局局長提出嘅」；赦膊嘅時候，佢就講「現屆政府跟進丁屋僭建工作嘅係財政司司長嘅下屬」。功就由佢嚟邀，鑊就射晒俾人，卷裝廁紙又唔識買，Ｆａｃｅｂｏｏｋ又要四個人教先識上，各位，林鄭月娥就係果隻香港打工仔最討厭最恐懼果隻Ａ字膊離地上司。<br />\n<br />\n俾大家揀，依啲咁嘅Ａ字膊廢老唔好話做特首，就算叫佢同咁多位打工仔同一間公司做嘢，我相信大家都要諗過先啦。你旨意佢上任之後會幫你搞標準工時、幫後生仔置業？佢唔話你後生仔唔捱得，想當年我地果代全靠獅子山精神先上到位，你已經要裝香還神啦！<br />\n<br />\n可惜，我地都冇得揀。"},{"pid":"9dc4548fe98af77608848f31ab3533f83b420812","tid":156374,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"乜僭建唔關政務司事咩？"},{"pid":"b25db667254dcc671cad0f96fa08e7e879e67cda","tid":156374,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/YoKhXe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2FYoKhXe&h=29eef955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/dAJf5c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2FdAJf5c&h=c2d82850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c46aa0ea3714a90a758cc96173cb31c0e36d140c","tid":156374,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w1y4crzi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw1y4crzi&h=f0b13edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w9cpt8ly\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw9cpt8ly&h=c45cc427&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}